import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';

const LogoContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: ${props => props.theme.spacing.sm};
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: ${props => props.theme.transitions.base};
  
  &:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
`;

const LogoIcon = styled.div`
  width: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  height: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
`;

const LogoText = styled.span`
  font-family: ${props => props.theme.fonts.primary};
  font-weight: ${props => props.theme.fontWeights.bold};
  font-size: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? props.theme.fontSizes['2xl'] : 
                        props.size === 'medium' ? props.theme.fontSizes.xl : 
                        props.theme.fontSizes.lg};
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.gradientPrimary};
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
`;

const LokanexLogo = ({ size = 'medium', showText = true, ...props }) => {
  return (
    <LogoContainer {...props}>
      <LogoIcon size={size}>
        <svg
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          viewBox="0 0 100 100"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          {/* Outer dynamic ring with tech pattern */}
          <circle
            cx="50"
            cy="50"
            r="42"
            stroke="url(#gradient1)"
            strokeWidth="1.5"
            fill="none"
            opacity="0.9"
          />
          
          {/* Inner hexagon for tech feel */}
          <polygon
            points="50,15 70,30 70,55 50,70 30,55 30,30"
            stroke="url(#gradient2)"
            strokeWidth="1.5"
            fill="none"
            opacity="0.7"
          />
          
          {/* Central L with modern twist */}
          <path
            d="M38 38 L38 58 L52 58 L52 50 L46 50 L46 44 L52 44"
            stroke="url(#gradient3)"
            strokeWidth="2.5"
            fill="none"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
          />
          
          {/* Floating tech elements */}
          <circle cx="20" cy="25" r="1.5" fill="#00d4ff" opacity="0.9">
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.9;0.3;0.9" dur="2s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </circle>
          <circle cx="80" cy="25" r="1.5" fill="#ff6b35" opacity="0.9">
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.3;0.9;0.3" dur="2s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </circle>
          <circle cx="20" cy="75" r="1.5" fill="#4ecdc4" opacity="0.9">
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.9;0.3;0.9" dur="2.5s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </circle>
          <circle cx="80" cy="75" r="1.5" fill="#00d4ff" opacity="0.9">
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.3;0.9;0.3" dur="2.5s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </circle>
          
          {/* Data flow lines */}
          <path
            d="M20 25 Q35 40 38 38"
            stroke="#00d4ff"
            strokeWidth="0.8"
            fill="none"
            opacity="0.6"
          >
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.6;0.2;0.6" dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </path>
          <path
            d="M80 25 Q65 40 52 44"
            stroke="#ff6b35"
            strokeWidth="0.8"
            fill="none"
            opacity="0.6"
          >
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.2;0.6;0.2" dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </path>
          <path
            d="M20 75 Q35 60 38 58"
            stroke="#4ecdc4"
            strokeWidth="0.8"
            fill="none"
            opacity="0.6"
          >
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.6;0.2;0.6" dur="3.5s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </path>
          <path
            d="M80 75 Q65 60 52 58"
            stroke="#00d4ff"
            strokeWidth="0.8"
            fill="none"
            opacity="0.6"
          >
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.2;0.6;0.2" dur="3.5s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </path>
          
          {/* Central glow effect */}
          <circle
            cx="50"
            cy="50"
            r="15"
            fill="url(#radialGlow)"
            opacity="0.3"
          />
          
          {/* Gradients */}
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="gradient1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="gradient2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="gradient3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="30%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="70%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="radialGlow" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" stopOpacity="0.4" />
              <stop offset="70%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" stopOpacity="0.2" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" stopOpacity="0.1" />
            </radialGradient>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </LogoIcon>
      {showText && <LogoText size={size}>Lokanex</LogoText>}
    </LogoContainer>
  );
};

export default LokanexLogo;
